Transition

a {
  color: black; /* Default link color */
  text-decoration: none; /* Optional: Removes the underline */
  transition: color 0.3s ease; /* Transition effect for the color property */
}

a:hover {
  color: red; /* Change to red on hover */
}

ease creates a smooth acceleration and deceleration effect.

linear is another option.

Src: chat > CSS List Spacing > "I want to add a transition css effect when hovered over a link to turn it red "
